Build tools required:
- Linaro GCC for 32-bit ARM
- GCC for your host

How to build:
export ARCH=arm
export SUBARCH=arm
export CROSS_COMPILE=`pwd`/toolchain/bin/arm-linux-gnueabihf-

make mrproper
make lux_defconfig
./build_twrp_zip.sh

You will now have a TWRP flashable zip at:
arch/arm/boot/moon_kernel.zip

Booting without isntalling:
fastboot boot arch/arm/boot/zImage
